title: Red Dwarf complete series ZUNE format (WMV)
description:
Well, here ya go. All 52 episodes from Red Dwarf&#039;s 8 seasons. I just got a Zune and after a few frustrating days I finally figured out a good formula for converting video files. These are all in WMV format and are ready to be sync&#039;d up with your zune, no extra conversion needed! They range from about 100-130 MB each, and they look great on my Zune. I&#039;ll post the technical details and some caps below. Enjoy!

AUDIO:
Audio Channel - Stereo
Sampling rate - 44100 frames/sec
Bit rate - 128 kbits/sec

VIDEO:
Frame rate - 29.97 frames/sec
Bit rate - 500 kbits/sec
Size - 320x240
